General.Name: Redwoods Acquisition Corp
General.Description: Redwoods Acquisition Corp. focuses on effecting a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, recapitalization, reorganization, or other similar business combination with one or more businesses or entities. In intends to focus on businesses in the carbon neutral and energy storage industries. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in New York, New York.
